author: Doha Madani
title: Popularity of Netflix's 'Tiger King' prompts sheriff to ask for leads in 1997 cold case
description: A Florida sheriff is jumping on the popularity of Netflix’s “Tiger King: Murder, Mayhem and Madness” series to ask for new leads in the 1997 disappearance of Jack Donald Lewis.
content:
